程序包 cn.sharesdk.demo

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AuthPage
    page to show how to authorize and get user info
    CustomerPage
    examples of custom interfaces
    DemoPage
    page to show how to use onekeyshare, how to get accse token, how to get user info etc.
    GetInforPage
    page shows how to request your or other user's info
    GetTokenPage
    page to show how to authorize and get accesstoken by sharesdk
    JsonPage
    page to display json data
    Laiwang  
    Laiwang.ShareParams  
    MainActivity
    entrance of the project, UI shell of sliding menu ui logics and events are handled by MainAdapter
    MainAdapter
    Adapter of sliding menu, handles ui events of sliding menu
    MyAdapter
    a example of AuthorizeAdapter the demo will display a "follow our official weibo" checkbox at the bottom of the auth-page.
    MyQZoneWebShareAdapter
    a example of QZoneWebShareAdapter
    OneKeyShareCallback
    onekeysharecallback is a example of "external callback" of onekeyshare.
    ShareContentCustomizeDemo
    OnekeyShare allows you to customize share content according to the target platform by implements ShareContentCustomizeCallback and override its #onShare(Platform, ShareParams) method This demo defines a callback to shorten share content of Twitter.
    SlidingMenuPage
    super-class of all sliding menu page
    WechatPage
    page to show Wechat apis.
    YixinPage
    page to show Yixin apis.
